content: Good morning Jeyachandran, it's nice to meet you. I'm Master, and I'm the hiring officer for this technical round. Based on your resume, I see you have an impressive background in AI, data engineering, and full-stack development. We'll be discussing your technical skills and experiences today. Let's get started! Can you tell me about your experience with React and Node.js in the development of the web app for mock interviews at Shine Logics?
